#: options_page.php:308
msgid ""
"The plugin allows you to feature the individual post as “breaking news.”."
msgstr ""

#: options_page.php:309
msgid ""
"Default title of the breaking news will be taken from the post title. But "
"you can also set a custom title for breaking news that will be shown instead "
"of the post title."
msgstr ""

#: options_page.php:310
msgid ""
"For breaking news post you can set an expiration date. When the required "
"time expires, the post will not be shown as “breaking news” at the site."
msgstr ""

#: options_page.php:311
msgid ""
"There can be only one active breaking news post at a time, which should be "
"the post that was activated last."
